{"TopicId":196206,"ForumId":21,"TopicTitle":"sas controlled starship fins prototype","CreatedByName":"Flying dutchman","CreatedById":189896,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-08-09T12:25:20Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Flying dutchman","CreatedById":189896,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-08-09T12:25:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022 data-embed-src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/TVE76Z2jVog?feature=oembed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-08-09T16:53:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nInteresting. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E Does it have a purpose or just for funsies?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Flying dutchman","CreatedById":189896,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-08-09T19:02:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223834932\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022196206\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221596992027\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002227914\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Vanamonde\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, Vanamonde said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nInteresting. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E Does it have a purpose or just for funsies?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nwell, the idea behind it is that it is normally impossible to make a starship controlled by \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Stability Augmentation System\u0022\u003Esas\u003C/abbr\u003E in ksp. if you were to attach\u00A0the normal control surfaces sideways they would not move. another idea is that you use the hinges from breaking ground and couple them with action groups to the pitch axis. you\u0027ll find however that, while you can then move those control surfaces, \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Stability Augmentation System\u0022\u003Esas\u003C/abbr\u003E has no influence on them so they can only be controlled manually which makes controlling the vessel very difficult. so to somewhat automate this process i\u0027ve used an aileron to power a set of levers and hinges that will move the fins the same way as starship does but controllable with \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Stability Augmentation System\u0022\u003Esas\u003C/abbr\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222020-08-09T19:03:52Z\u0022 title=\u002208/09/2020 07:03  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 9, 2020\u003C/time\u003E by Flying dutchman\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}